name: Elrond [LotR] Mini Dude #123
description: Elrond Half-elven, Lord of Rivendell, was one of the mighty Elf-rulers of old who lived in Middle-earth from the First Age to the beginning of the Fourth Age. He was the father of Arwen Undomiel, the eventual lover of Aragorn II Elessar. [https://lotr.fandom.com/wiki/Elrond]
